Whosoever keepeth his duty to Allâh, Allâh will appoint a way out for
him,

And will provide for him in a way that he cannot foresee. And
whosoever putteth his trust in Allâh, He will suffice him. Lo! Allâh
bringeth His command to pass. Allâh hath set a measure for all things.
